Repository contain my experiments with android native activity

Requirements for build:
1. Android NDK
2. Android CMake - i recommend this: https://github.com/taka-no-me/android-cmake

Instruction for install Android CMake view on my blog http://ingener74.blogspot.ru/ - the message about it not ready but i am write it in the close time

3rdparty contained: 
1. OpenCV 2.4.4-beta for Android

build programs: for example i show on "opengles_test"
in ${REPO_HOME} in console type next
1. > cd opengles_test
2. > mkdir build
3. > cd build
4. > android-cmake .. 
5. > make

then program maked

6. create Android Application in eclipse: for example in ~/workspace/RotatingCube/
7. > cp -R ../libs ~/workspace/RotatingCube
8. Edit AndroidManifest.xml in Android application like ${REPO_HOME}/tools/AndroidManifest.xml
9. Run as Android application... RotatingCube
10. Enjoy :)

P. S. Sorry for my terrible English ))
